      <title>美国薪资最高预测，失业率为4.2％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/us-payrolls-top-forecasts-unemployment-rate-at-4-2-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着3月份非农业薪资增长228,000，随着参与率提高，失业率提高了4.2％，美国就业增长速度的预测率提高了4.2％。迈克尔·麦基（Michael McKee）分解了彭博电视台（Bloomberg Television）上的数字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/us-payrolls-top-forecasts-unemployment-rate-at-4-2-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:47:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行率切入的赌注成为增长最高关税的最高限额清单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/ecb-rate-cut-bets-build-as-growth-tops-list-of-tariff-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者和分析师评估唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）关税的影响，对欧洲中央银行利率削减的期望正在上升，得出的结论是，通货膨胀结果将更加良性，而增长会受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/ecb-rate-cut-bets-build-as-growth-tops-list-of-tariff-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗杰斯向养老金支持的黑石基金出售50亿美元的网络股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/rogers-sells-5-billion-network-stake-to-pension-backed-blackstone-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗杰斯通讯公司（Rogers Communications Inc.）同意将其无线网络中的股份出售给由黑石公司（Blackstone Inc.）管理的资金，该资金在70亿加元（49亿加元）的股权交易中得到了四项加拿大养老金的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/rogers-sells-5-billion-network-stake-to-pension-backed-blackstone-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:33:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>JPM的Misra认为在关税市场上看到了“希望贸易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/jpm-s-misra-sees-hope-trade-in-markets-on-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通（JPMorgan）的投资组合经理普里亚·米斯拉（Priya Misra）表示，在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税宣布之后，投资者正在依靠许多希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/jpm-s-misra-sees-hope-trade-in-markets-on-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:23:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲的银行在增长困境中失去了表现最佳的部门王冠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-s-banks-lose-best-performing-sector-crown-on-growth-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易关税引起了衰退的问题，银行不再是欧洲表现最佳的部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-s-banks-lose-best-performing-sector-crown-on-growth-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:18:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
